    {
      "logical_unit_id": "MD12056_lu20",
      "document_id": "MD12056",
      "title": "(iii) In all the above cases (excepting shortages in chest balances / remittances,",
      "text": "(iii) In all the above cases (excepting shortages in chest balances / remittances,\nshortages due to pilferage / frauds, counterfeit banknotes detected in chest balances /\nremittances), penal interest will be levied from the date of inclusion of 'ineligible'\namounts in chest balances till the exclusion of such amounts from chest balances.\nPenal measures for shortages in chest balances / remittances, shortages due to\npilferage / frauds, counterfeit banknotes detected in chest balances / remittances will be\ntaken on the basis of prevailing \"Scheme of Penalties\".\n2 Levy of penalty",
      "node_type": "subclause",
      "level": 6,
      "page_range": [
